sted%20For%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO's%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2026-year-old%20man%20was%20arrested%20Monday%20over%20the%20targeted%20killing%20of%20a%20health%20insurance%20executive%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20New%20York%2C%20with%20investigators%20charging%20him%20with%20possession%20of%20fake%20IDs%20and%20a%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20continued%20to%20interrogate%20Luigi%20Mangione%20in%20connection%20with%20last%20week's%20brazen%20murder%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20nationwide%20manhunt%20and%20global%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20arrived%20at%20a%20Pennsylvania%20court%20wearing%20a%20dark%20sweatshirt%20after%206%3A00%20pm%20(2300%20GMT)%20Monday%20and%20was%20led%20inside%20by%20Altoona%20police%20flanked%20by%20NYPD%20detectives%20where%20he%20was%20arraigned%2C%20broadcasters%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20is%20next%20due%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20on%20December%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPennsylvania%20Governor%20Josh%20Shapiro%20said%20that%20murder%20charges%20in%20New%20York%20state%20would%20follow%2C%20telling%20a%20media%20briefing%20%26quot%3Bwe%20do%20not%20kill%20people%20in%20cold%20blood%20to%20resolve%20policy%20differences%20or%20express%20a%20viewpoint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20not%20confirmed%20reports%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bdelay%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeny%26quot%3B%20--%20language%20used%20by%20insurers%20to%20reject%20claims%20--%20were%20written%20on%20casings%20found%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20hinting%20at%20a%20possible%20political%20motive%20for%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20was%20apprehended%20by%20officers%20following%20a%20tip%20from%20staff%20at%20an%20Altoona%20McDonald's%20branch%2C%20where%20he%20was%20found%20wearing%20a%20mask%20and%20a%20beanie%20while%20using%20a%20laptop%2C%20and%20gave%20officers%20a%20fake%20ID%2C%20charging%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20searched%20him%20and%20found%20what%20police%20