C%22f2b78499-2b24-45d9-ae32-324c4a19dbc2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20relationship%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20whirlwind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20met%20in%20December%2C%20got%20engaged%20in%20August%2C%20and%20married%20the%20next%20December.%20It%20may%20seem%20fast%20to%20some%20people%2C%20but%20we%20both%20knew%20we%20had%20found%20the%20one%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20spend%20our%20lives%20with.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20summer%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fengagement-ring-trends-2024-styles-designs-jewelers-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20engaged%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20couldn't%20imagine%20having%20a%20piece%20of%20jewelry%20that%20had%20so%20much%20significance%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20wear%20every%20day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20having%20any%20input%2C%20so%20we%20went%20ring%20shopping%20together.%20Initially%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20pick%20a%20style%20I%20liked%20and%20then%20he%20would%20pick%20out%20the%20ring.%20Then%20I%20found%20a%20ring%20that%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20told%20me%20he%20had%20ordered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-budget-big-engagement-ring-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ring%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20he%20had%20planned%20for%20the%20proposal.%20I%20don't%20love%20surprises%2C%20so%20something%20elaborate%2C%20embarrassing%2C%20or%20public%20was%20definitely%20out%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20knew%20that.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22595044fa-f584-45c8-a496-b049c7fb7baf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20weekend%20away%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20time%20for%20a%20proposal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20weekend%20of%20August%20we%20drove%20a%20few%20hours%20away%20so%20my%20now-husband%20could%20fill%20in%20with%20a%20quartet%20that%20he%20used%20to%20sing%20with.%20I%20went%20into%20that%20trip%20with%20a%20feeling%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20propose.%20But%20as%20we%20were%20driving%20home%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20weekend%20and%20day%20turned%20into%20night%20I%20figured%20it%20probably%20wasn't%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20which%20was%20disappointing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20a%20song%20came%20on%20as%20we%20were%20driving%20through%20rural%20Delaware.%20It%20was%20%26quot%3BI%20Could%20Not%20Ask%20for%20More%26quot%3B%20by%20Edwin%20McCain%2C%20and%20he%20sang%20it%20to%20me.%20After%20the%20song%20was%20finished%2C%20he%20told%20me%20how%20much%20he%20loved%20me%20and%20how%20he%20could%20never%20ask%20for%20anything%20more.%20It%20sounded%20like%20a%20proposal%20speech%2C%20but%20no%20proposal%20came.%20He%20just%20said%20he%20wished%20he%20wasn't%20driving%20so%20he%20could%20hug%20me.%20I%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20you%20could%20just%20pull%20over%20and%20propose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222899%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Selfie%20of%20couple%20with%20an%20ocean%20backdrop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6751d08134ef9f0108f4e9fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222174%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20Tom%20while%20on%20a%20roadtrip%20in%20California%20in%202017.%3Cp%3ESara%20Rowe%20Mount%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c079b70-1f29-473e-80f7-4ce4eed5eb36%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20proposal%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20surprise%2C%20even%20to%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20mile%20up%20the%20road%2C%20he%20pulled%20off%20into%20a%20Holiday%20Inn%20Express%20parking%20lot%20as%20I%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%20After%20all%2C%20I%20hadn't%20been%20completely%20serious%20about%20pulling%20over.%20Turns%20out%2C%20he%20was.%20He%20parked%2C%20reached%20over%20and%20hugged%20me%20as%20he%20rooted%20in%20the%20back%20seat%20for%20something.%20That's%20when%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20happening.%20There%20sitting%20in%20the%20front%20seat%20of%20his%20car%20in%20a%20hotel%20parking%20lot%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20be%20his%20forever.%20I%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20commented%20that%20he%20hadn't%20gotten%20down%20on%20one%20knee.%20So%20he%20took%20the%20ring%20off%20my%20finger%2C%20went%20around%20to%20my%20side%20of%20the%20car%2C%20got%20down%20one%20knee%2C%20and%20proposed%20again.%20He%20was%20crying%2C%20but%20I%20was%20so%20excited%20I%20just%20started%20laughing%20and%20jumping%20up%20and%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20the%20entire%20thing%20was%20pretty%20on%20brand%20for%20our%20quirky%2C%20goofy%20relationship.%20There%20may%20not%20have%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-romantic-restaurants-in-the-us-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eromantic%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20flowers%20and%20champagne%20or%20a%20scavenger%20hunt%20that%20had%20been%20planned%20out%20for%20weeks%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20really%20mind.%20Yes%2C%20the%20proposal%20was%20spur%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20but%20I%20still%20think%20it%20was%20pretty%20romantic%2C%20even%20now%20that%20we've%20been%20married%20for%20nine%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-got-engaged-in-parking-lot-unique-untraditional-proposal-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733790482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6751d04334ef9f0108f4e9ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-got-engaged-in-parking-lot-unique-untraditional-proposal-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20parking%20lot%20engagement%20wasn't%20what%20I%20ever%20expected%2C%20but%20it%20was%20perfect%20for%20us.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sara%20Rowe%20Mount)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonic