20what%20to%20know%20about%20Mangione%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f0afa31-973c-464b-85df-7813f3e4bcd0%5C%22%3EMangione%20attended%20elite%20schools%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20achieved%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Science%20in%20Engineering%20with%20a%20major%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20a%20minor%20in%20mathematics.%20He%20also%20received%20a%20Master%20of%20Science%20in%20Engineering%20the%20same%20year%20with%20a%20major%20in%20computer%20and%20information%20science%2C%20a%20university%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%20he%20attended%20Gilman%20School%2C%20an%20elite%20all-boys%20preparatory%20school%20based%20in%20Baltimore.%20His%20yearbook%20entry%2C%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20says%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20robotics%20and%20Model%20UN.%20He%20wrote%20on%20his%20LinkedIn%20account%20that%20he%20was%20the%20valedictorian%20of%20his%20high%20school%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokeswoman%20for%20Gilman%20didn't%20immediately%20return%20a%20voicemail%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c35bec8b-d509-482a-8982-352e94f59191%5C%22%3EHe%20favorably%20reviewed%20The%20Unabomber%20Manifesto%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Goodreads%2C%20Mangione%20reviewed%20Ted%20Kaczynski's%20%26quot%3BIndustrial%20Society%20and%20Its%20Future%26quot%3B%20book%2C%20also%20known%20as%20The%20Unabomber%20Manifesto%2C%20in%20early%202024.%20He%20gave%20it%20four%20out%20of%20five%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20violent%20individual%20%E2%80%94%20rightfully%20imprisoned%20%E2%80%94%20who%20maimed%20innocent%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mangione%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20these%20actions%20tend%20to%20be%20characterized%20as%20those%20of%20a%20crazy%20luddite%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20more%20accurately%20seen%20as%20those%20of%20an%20extreme%20political%20revolutionary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione's%20review%20of%20the%20manifesto%20also%20quoted%20another%20online%20comment%20about%20the%20book%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20have%20originated%20on%20Reddit%2C%20praising%20the%20use%20of%20violence%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20all%20other%20forms%20of%20communication%20fail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Violence%20never%20solved%20anything'%20is%20a%20statement%20uttered%20by%20cowards%20and%20predators%2C'%26quot%3B%20Mangione%20quoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c32f3f87-d884-4392-ab2b-dcf3b7535440%5C%22%3EOnline%20breadcrumbs%20suggest%20he%20dealt%20with%20back%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20Mangione's%20profile%20on%20X%20%E2%80%94%20formerly%20Twitter%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20triptych%20of%20three%20images%3A%20a%20photo%20of%20himself%2C%20smiling%2C%20shirtless%20on%20a%20mountain%20ridge%3B%20a%20Pokemon%3B%20and%20an%20x-ray%20with%20four%20pins%20or%20screws%20visible%20in%20the%20lower%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20books%20reviewed%20on%20Mangione's%20Goodreads%20account%20related%20to%20health%20and%20healing%20back%20pain%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BBack%20Mechanic%3A%20The%20Secrets%20to%20a%20Healthy%20Spine%20Your%20Doctor%20Isn't%20Telling%20You%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCrooked%3A%20Outwitting%20the%20Back%20Pain%20Industry%20and%20Getting%20on%20the%20Road%20to%20Recovery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pokemon%20featured%20in%20his%20X%20cover%20image%2C%20next%20to%20an%20apparent%20spinal%20X-ray%2C%20is%20Breloom.%20In%20the%20Pokemon%20games%2C%20it%20has%20special%20healing%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df1d633d-f569-475a-a6e1-4750c613b960%5C%22%3EHe%20founded%20an%20app%20and%20worked%20in%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20still%20in%20high%20school%2C%20in%202015%2C%20Mangione%20founded%20a%20company%20called%20AppRoar%20Studios.%20AppRoar%20released%20an%20iPhone%20game%20called%20Pivot%20Plane%20that%20is%20no%20longer%20available%2C%20but%20a%20reviewer%20in%202015%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20fun%20little%20arcade%20game%20brought%20to%20you%20by%203%20high%20school%20juniors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20lived%20in%20a%20coliving%20space%20in%20Hawaii%20as%20recently%20as%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20posed%20for%20photos%20indicating%20he%20participated%20in%20Greek%20life%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fraternity%20chapter%20represented%20in%20his%20photos%20couldn't%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cofounded%20a%20video%20game%20design%20club%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20according%20to%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania's%20website%20that%20was%20removed%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Lane%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20video%20game%20design%20at%20the%20Ivy%20League%20university%2C%20who%20did%20not%20advise%20the%20club%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fact%20he%20took%20the%20initiative%20and%20started%20something%20from%20nothing%2C%20that%20means%20at%20least%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Penn%2C%20that's%20a%20pretty%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20the%20shooting%20of%20Thompson%2C%20Lane%20added%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20not%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20Mangione%20worked%20as%20a%20data%20engineer%20at%20the%20vehicle%20shopping%20company%20TrueCar%20starting%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20TrueCar%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20Mangione%20has%20not%20worked%20for%20the%20company%20since%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22169a21b5-2309-4626-8e9e-d6d66b4f7967%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20previously%20cited%20for%20trespassing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20had%20at%20least%20one%20encounter%20with%20the%20legal%20system%20before%20his%20Monday%20arrest.%20Hawaiian%20court%20records%20indicate%20that%20he%20was%20cited%20in%202023%20for%20entering%20a%20forbidden%20area%20of%20a%20state%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20appears%20to%20have%20paid%20a%20%24100%20fine%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e9da71e-2188-4fb2-81b1-89cb5ab41073%5C%22%3EMangione%20was%20interested%20in%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20X%20account%2C%20Mangione%20posted%20and%20amplified%20posts%20about%20technological%20advances%20like%20artificial%20intelligence.%20He%20also%20posted%20about%20fitness%20and%20healthy%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20frequently%20reposted%20posts%20by%20the%20writer%20Tim%20Urban%20and%20commentator%20Jonathan%20Haidt%20about%20the%20promise%20and%20perils%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20fan%20of%20Michael%20Pollan%2C%20known%20for%20his%20writing%20about%20food%20and%20ethics%2C%20and%20lab-grown%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Goodreads%2C%20he%20praised%20Urban's%20book%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20Our%20Problem%3F%3A%20A%20Self-Help%20Book%20for%20Societies%2C%26quot%3B%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20important%20philosophical%20texts%20of%20the%20early%2021st%20century.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUrban%20posted%20to%20X%20on%20Monday%3A%20%26quot%3BVery%20much%20not%20the%20point%20of%20the%20book.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd7ccff4-78e9-4d4d-a4aa-48628c698b25%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20while%20on%20his%20laptop%20at%20a%20McDonald's%2C%20police%20said%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20police%20in%20Altoona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20responded%20to%20a%20McDonald's%20after%20a%20call%20about%20a%20suspicious%20person%2C%20they%20found%20Mangione%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20looking%20at%20a%20silver%20laptop%20and%20wearing%20a%20blue%20medical%20mask%2C%20according%20to%20a%20criminal%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20that%20when%20asked%20for%20identification%2C%20Mangione%20gave%20police%20officers%20a%20New%20Jersey%20driver's%20license%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BMark%20Rosario.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20officer%20asked%20Mangione%20if%20he%20had%20been%20to%20New%20York%