%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20restaurant%20scene%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20try%20something%20different.%20They%20share%20the%20same%20vision%3A%20to%20raise%20the%20standard%20of%20food%20in%20aged%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20working%20under%20top%20chefs%2C%20including%20Donovan%20Cooke%2C%20Shen%20had%20also%20picked%20up%20shifts%20at%20Australian%20nursing%20homes%20in%20the%20past.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20time%20that%20he%20noticed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-frozen-meals-tasty-healthy-expensive-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrozen%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20often%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20he%20saw%20a%20job%20posting%20from%20St%20Vincent's%20for%20a%20chef%20to%20elevate%20nursing%20home%20food%2C%20it%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20do.%20To%20change%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a49ed603-94f8-4ad6-90a2-84fe80b830a0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20premium%20offering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Shen%20on%20board%2C%20Martin%20and%20his%20team%20worked%20during%20the%20pandemic%20to%20reinvent%20meal%20plans%20at%20one%20of%20St%20Vincent's%20healthcare%20centers%20in%20Kew%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralia-real-estate-home-auctions-america-buy-sell-bidding-wars-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelbourne%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20facility%20doubles%20as%20an%20aged%20care%20home%20and%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20more%20premium%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproblems-with-nursing-homes-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enursing%20home%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20St%20Vincent's%20Care's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.svcs.org.au%2Fresidential-aged-care%2Fvic%2Fmelbourne%2Fkew%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%