idents%20who%20have%20dysphagia%2C%20a%20geriatric%20syndrome%20that%20affects%20swallowing.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinicproceedings.org%2Farticle%2FS0025-6196(20)30902-2%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMayo%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2010%25%20to%2033%25%20of%20older%20adults%20have%20dysphagia%20and%20can%20face%20malnutrition%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20the%20chefs%20provide%20a%20range%20of%20options%20for%20residents%20with%20different%20needs%20so%20that%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20even%20those%20who%20struggle%20to%20swallow%20%E2%80%94%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-diet-food-list-cheap-easy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenjoy%20a%20hearty%20meal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6498372-fc46-43a1-8381-63963da6155a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENursing%20home%20food%20on%20the%20world%20stage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20and%20Shen%20wanted%20to%20show%20the%20world%20that%20nursing%20home%20food%20can%20%E2%80%94%20and%20should%20%E2%80%94%20be%20just%20as%20good%20as%20restaurant%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20compete%20in%20culinary%20competitions%20together.%20After%20placing%20in%20several%20local%20competitions%2C%20they%20were%20approached%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20International%20Salon%20Culinaire%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchopped-interesting-things-you-never-knew-from-someone-on-show-2022-03%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompetitions%20for%20chefs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Previous%20winners%20of%20the%20competition%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-is-hells-kitchen-restaurant-worth-it-for-couple-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGordon%20Ramsey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Michael%20Deane%2C%20a%20Michelin-star%20chef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20this%2