on%20Picture%20in%20a%20Non-English%20Language.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fgolden-globes-2025-nominations-jacques-audiards-emilia-prez-payal-kapadias-all-we-imagine-as-light-and-others-make-it-to-the-list%2Farticleshow%2F116148410.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCondemn%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20E%20Shinde%20After%20Karnataka%20Cancels%20Maratha%20Conference%20Approval%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Monday%20criticised%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20for%20denying%20permission%20to%20'Marathi%20Ekikaran%20Samiti'%20to%20hold%20their%20conference%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20accused%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Brepressing%26quot%3B%20the%20Maratha%20community%20by%20arresting%20several%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMarathi-speaking%20people%20in%20Karnataka%20had%20organised%20a%20conference.%20In%20this%20country%2C%20one%20can%20live%20anywhere%2C%20go%20anywhere%20and%20organise%20a%20conference%2C%20but%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20unleashed%20a%20cycle%20of%20repression%20and%20arrested%20the%20MLA%2C%20mayor%20and%20more%20than%20100%20Marathi-speaking%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20the%20Marathi%20Ekikaran%20Samiti%20who%20had%20organised%20the%20conference.%20I%20condemn%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20emphasized%20that%20Veer%20Savarkar%2C%20who%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20for%20the%20country%2C%20should%20be%20respected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20condemn%20those%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20remove%20his%20statue...%20Our%20stand%20is%20clear%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20will%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20which%20is%20resorting%20to%20such%20repression%2C%26quot%3B%20Shinde%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Aditya%20Thackeray%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20incident%20and%20demanded%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Binjustice%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Marathi%20people%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Karnataka%20government%20not%20only%20denied%20permission%20to%20the%20General%20Conference%20of%20Maharashtra%20Integration%20Committee%20being%20held%20in%20Belgaum%20but%20also%20imposed%20a%20curfew%20in%20Belgaum.%20Borders%20are%20also%20being%20closed.%20Strong%20protest%20against%20this%20injustice%20on%20Marathi%20people!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBelgaum%20is%20and%20will%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Marathi%20identity!%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Karnataka%20to%20stop%20this%20injustice%20to%20the%20Marathi%20people%20immediately!%20Nothing%20is%20greater%20than%20the%20interest%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Marathi%20people!%26quot%3B%20Thackeray%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MLA%20said%20that%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20support%20the%20proposal%20to%20make%20Belgaum%2C%20a%20union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20unanimously%20support%20the%20proposal%20to%20make%20Belgaum%20a%20union%20territory%20for%20the%20justice%20of%20the%20Marathi%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Ambadas%20Danve%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20any%20party%20issue%20but%20a%20Maratha%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20party%20issue%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20or%20Shiv%20Sena%20issue.%20This%20is%20a%20Marathi%20Manoos%20issue.%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20always%20taken%20the%20right%20stand%20for%20Marathis%2C%20Aditya%20Thackeray%20has%20taken%20it...%20Our%20priority%20is%20that%20Marathi%20Manoos%20who%20are%20in%20Belgaum%20of%20Karnataka%20should%20be%20given%20security%20and%20they%20should%20get%20the%20rights%20they%20have%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20BJP%20government%20here%20and%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20so%20if%20injustice%20is%20being%20done%20to%20Marathi%20Manoos%20then%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20Maharashtra%20should%20take%20steps%20for%20it.%20Veer%20Savarkar%20is%20a%20brave%20freedom%20fighter%20not%20only%20of%20Maharashtra%20but%20of%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20his%20contribution%20is%20huge%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20wrong%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20to%20remove%20Veer%20Savarkar's%20picture%20from%20the%20legislature%2C%20they%20have%20not%20removed%20it%20yet%20but%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20should%20clearly%20state%20its%20stand%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20doing%20so%2C%20this%20is%20our%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20Danve%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733768700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fj1jmcmio_eknath-shinde_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcondemn-this-eknath-shinde-after-karnataka-cancels-maratha-conference-approval-7211084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Monday%20criticised%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20for%20denying%20permission%20to%20'Marathi%20Ekikaran%20Samiti'%20to%20hold%20their%20conference%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcondemn-this-eknath-shinde-after-karnataka-cancels-maratha-conference-approval-7211084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20at%20Aaliyah-Shane's%20pre-wedding%20cocktail%20party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733768562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116148029%2Cimgsize-100010.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faaliyah-kashyap-shane-gregoire-pre-wedding-khushi-kapoor-vedang-raina-ibrahim-ali-khan-alaya-f-aaishvary-thackeray-and-others-attend-their-cocktail-party%2Farticleshow%2F116148029.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116148029.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAaliyah%20Kashyap%2C%20daughter%20of%20filmmaker%20Anurag%20Kashyap%2C%20celebrated%20her%20upcoming%20wedding%20with%20boyfriend%20Shane%20Gregoire%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20couple%20hosted%20a%20pre-wedding%20bash%20attended%20by%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20Bollywood%20personalities.%20Aaliyah%20stunned%20in%20a%20red%20lehenga%2C%20while%20Shane%20opted%20for%20a%20black%20bandhgala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faaliyah-kashyap-shane-gregoire-pre-wedding-khushi-kapoor-vedang-raina-ibrahim-ali-khan-alaya-f-aaishvary-thackeray-and-others-attend-their-cocktail-party%2Farticleshow%2F116148029.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Russia-Made%20Warship%20Comes%20With%20Ukrainian%20Engines.%20How%20It%20Happened%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20years-long%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20Moscow%20and%20Kiev%20worked%20separately%20for%20a%20common%20cause%20-%20to%20manufacture%20an%20Indian%20Navy%20warship%2C%20which%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20when%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20arrived%20in%20Moscow%20for%20a%20top-level%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20frigate%20-%20INS%20Tushil%20-%20is%20one%20of%20two%20naval%20ships%20for%20which%20India%20placed%20an%20order%20with%20Russia%20in%202016.%20It%20is%20a%20Krivak%20III-class%20warship%2C%20which%20is%20an%20advanced%20stealth%20missile%20frigate.%20India%20currently%20operates%20six%20such%20warships%20-%20all%20manufactured%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20two%20that%20is%20being%20made%20in%20Russia%2C%20two%20more%20similar%20ships%20have%20been%20ordered%20to%20be%20manufactured%20in%20India%20and%20will%20likely%20be%20manufactured%20at%20the%20Goa%20Shipyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20interesting%20is%20that%20the%20primary%20engines%20-%20the%20gas%20turbines%20of%20these%20frigates%20-%20is%20manufactured%20in%20Ukraine.%20A%20Russian%20warship%20with%20a%20Ukrainian%20engine%2C%20made%20for%20India%20-%20which%20shares%20close%20ties%20with%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fu4eqkrd8_ins-tushil-ceremony_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20the%20ships%20in%20the%20Indian%20navy%20fleet%20use%20gas%20turbines%20made%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20company%20Zorya-Mashproekt%20-%20which%20is%20a%20recognised%20globally%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20marine%20gas%20turbine%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20unique%20however%2C%20is%20that%20this%20order%20has%20been%20delivered%20while%20the%20war%20is%20on%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20it%20is%20significant%20to%20note%20that%20both%20countries%20have%20delivered%20the%20order%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20conflict.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20challenge%20involved%20-%20India%20had%20to%20physically%20procure%20these%20engines%20from%20Ukraine%20and%20have%20them%20delivered%20to%20Russia%20before%20they%20could%20be%20installed%20on%20this%20warship%2C%20so%20it%20has%20been%20somewhat%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EALL%20ABOUT%20THE%20INS%20TUSHIL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Tushil%20is%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20latest%20multi-role%2C%20stealth-guided%20missile%20frigate.%20The%20name%20'Tushil'%20means%20a%20'protector%20shield'%20and%20its%20crest%20represents%20the%20'Abhedya%20Kavacham'%20(Impenetrable%20Shield).%20It%20has%20a%20motto%20-%20'Nirbhay%2C%20Abhedya%20aur%20Balsheel'%20(Fearless%2C%20Indomitable%2C%20and%20Resolute).%20The%20ship%20stands%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20undying%20commitment%20to%20safeguarding%20the%20nation's%20maritime%20frontiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INS%20Tushil%20is%20an%20advanced%20Russian%20Krivak%20III-class%20warship%20under%20'Project%2011356'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fbpnt3vr8_ins-tushil_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%2011356%20is%20the%20code%20name%20for%20the%20Talwar-class%20frigates%2C%20which%20are%20a%20class%20of%20stealth%2C%20guided-missile%20frigates%20designed%20and%20built%20by%20Russia%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20The%20design%20for%20the%20Talwar%20Class%20frigates%20have%20been%20developed%20as%20an%20advanced%20version%20of%20the%20Admiral%20Grigorovich-class%20frigates%20that%20Russia%20uses.%20So%20far%2C%20six%20such%20ships%20have%20been%20built%20and%20delivered%20by%20Russia%20to%20India%20between%201999%20and%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20Krivak%20class%20warships%20that%20are%20already%20in%20service%20are%203%20Talwar%20Class%20ships%20built%20at%20Baltiysky%20shipyard%20in%20St.%20Petersburg%2C%20and%20three%20Teg%20Class%20ships%20constructed%20at%20the%20Yantar%20shipyard%20in%20Kaliningrad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'INS%20Tushil'%20will%20be%20the%20seventh%20in%20the%20series%2C%20and%20the%20first%20of%20the%20two%20upgraded%2C%20advanced%20warships%20for%20which%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20had%20signed%20a%20contract%20with%20Russia's%20JSC%20Rosoboronexport%2C%20in%20October%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhp6vc2b_ins-tushil_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20125-metre-long%20warship%2C%20weighing%203%2C900%20tonnes%2C%20was%20under%20constant%20monitoring%20by%20experts%20of%20India's%20Warship%20Overseeing%20Team%20stationed%20permanently%20in%20Russia's%20Kaliningrad%20throughout%20its%20construction.%20The%20warship%20is%20fitted%20with%20advanced%20Indian%20missiles%2C%20details%20of%20which%20are%20not%20revealed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warship%20has%20undergone%20a%20series%20of%20sea%20trials%2C%20factory%20sea%20trials%2C%20and%20state%20committee%20trials%20starting%20January%202024%2C%20during%20which%20it%20clocked%20an%20impressive%20speed%20of%20more%20than%2030%20knots%20(55%20kmph).%20It%20is%20now%20being%20delivered%20to%20India%20in%20a%20combat-ready%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20delivering%20the%20warship%20to%20India%20at%20Kaliningrad%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20along%20with%20Indian%20Navy%20Chief%20Admiral%20Dinesh%20K%20Tripathi%20will%20be%20commissioning%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20commissioning%2C%20INS%20Tushil%20will%20join%20the%20'Sword%20Arm'%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20the%20Western%20Fleet%2C%20under%20the%20Western%20Naval%20Command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20CHINA%20CHALLENGE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20of%20the%20two%20warships%20have%20been%20delivered%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20delivery%20date%20for%20the%20second%20ship%20might%20take%20a%20while.%20The%20warship%20is%20an%20important%20addition%20to%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20which%20is%20faced%20with%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20fast-growing%20Chinese%20Navy%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20Navy%20is%20the%20fastest-growing%20navy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20according%20to%20some%20reports%20the%20Chinese%20Navy%20might%20have%20already%20outnumbered%20the%20US%20Navy%20to%20become%20the%20largest%20naval%20fleet%20globally.%20Nowhere%20is%20this%20felt%20more%20significantly%20that%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20the%20geographical%20advantage%20over%20China%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20its%20strategic%20location%20close%20to%20key%20choke%20points%20leading%20to%20it%2C%20China%20has%20the%20advantage%20in%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20vessels%20in%20the%20naval%20fleet.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733768520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fbpnt3vr8_ins-tushil_625x300_09_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fins-tushil-russia-ukraine-come-together-despite-war-to-deliver-navy-ship-to-india-7210940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20years-long%20war%20between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20Moscow%20and%20Kiev%20worked%20separately%20for%20a%20common%20cause%20-%20to%20manufacture%20an%20Indian%20Navy%20warship%2C%20which%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20when%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20arrived%20in%20Moscow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonical