lled%2C%2017%20Injured%20After%20Bus%20Rams%20Vehicles%2C%20Residential%20Gate%20In%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2017%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20state-run%20bus%20rammed%20some%20vehicles%20on%20a%20busy%20road%20in%20Mumbai's%20Kurla%20(West)%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20shows%20the%20red%20bus%20barrelling%20down%20the%20road%20at%20a%20high%20speed.%20The%20first%20vehicle%20it%20rammed%20was%20an%20autorickshaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brakes%20of%20the%20BEST%20bus%20may%20have%20failed%2C%20a%20municipal%20corporation%20official%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20people%20have%20been%20admitted%20to%20Sion%20and%20Kurla%20Bhabha%20Hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20happened%20at%209.50%20pm.%20The%20BEST%20bus%20route%20number%20332%20was%20going%20from%20Kurla%20station%20to%20Andheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Brihanmumbai%20Electric%20Supply%20and%20Transport%20Undertaking%2C%20or%20BEST%2C%20provides%20transport%20service%20to%20the%20entire%20city%20and%20also%20extends%20its%20operations%20outside%20city%20limits%20into%20neighbouring%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20the%20bus%20driver%20lost%20control%20and%20rammed%20some%20pedestrians%20and%20vehicles.%20It%20then%20crashed%20into%20the%20gates%20of%20a%20residential%20complex%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20eyewitness%20to%20the%20BEST%20bus%20crash%20said%20it%20was%20swerving%20over%20a%20stretch%20of%20200%20metres%20before%20the%20accident.%20Zaid%20Ahmed%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20resident%20of%20the%20area%2C%20said%20he%20was%20leaving%20his%20house%20to%20go%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20when%20he%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ran%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20saw%20a%20BEST%20bus%20had%20hit%20pedestrians%2C%20other%20vehicles%2C%20including%20an%20autorickshaw%20and%20three%20cars.%20I%20saw%20some%20bodies.%20We%20rescued%20the%20passengers%20in%20the%20autorickshaw%20and%20took%20them%20to%20Bhabha%20Hospital%20in%20another%20three-wheeler.%20My%20friends%20also%20helped%20in%20providing%20relief%20to%20the%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ahmed%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20eyewitnesses%20said%20the%20bus%20also%20rammed%20a%20police%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20was%20a%2012-metre-long%20electric%20bus%20manufactured%20by%20Olectra%20and%20it%20had%20been%20taken%20by%20BEST%20on%20a%20wet%20lease%2C%20another%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20drivers%20of%20such%20buses%20are%20supplied%20by%20the%20private%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bus%20is%20just%20three%20months%20old.%20It%20was%20registered%20on%20August%2020%20this%20year%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20called%20EVEY%20Trans%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Tardeo%20regional%20transport%20office%20(RTO)%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733768160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgvgvvdo8_best-bus-accident_625x300_09_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-people-killed-17-injured-after-state-bus-rams-vehicles-in-mumbai-7210709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2017%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20state-run%20bus%20rammed%20some%20vehicles%20on%20a%20road%20in%20Mumbai's%20Kurla%20(West)%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-people-killed-17-injured-after-state-bus-rams-vehicles-in-mumbai-7210709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BP%20forms%20offshore%20wind%20JV%20with%20Japan's%20JERA%20in%20renewables%20retreat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733767847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbp-forms-offshore