%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20of%20the%20Opposition%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20anti-India%20rhetoric%20used%20by%20US%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20remarked%20India's%20former%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Kanwal%20Sibal%2C%20amid%20BJP%20allegations%20of%20top%20Congress%20leaders%20colluding%20with%20Soros%20to%20destabilise%20the%20country.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20while%20the%20US%20and%20a%20section%20within%20it%20are%20favourably%20disposed%20towards%20India%20as%20a%20counter-balance%20to%20China%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20section%20which%20is%20out%20to%20damage%20India's%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20well-known%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20the%20deep%20state%20in%20the%20United%20States%20--%20agencies%20and%20personnel%2C%20academics%20and%20think%20tanks%20--%20is%20attacking%20India%20very%20viciously%2C%20which%20finds%20expression%20in%20the%20media%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20this%20consistent%20line%20of%20bringing%20India's%20democracy%20into%20disrepute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20this%20campaign%20against%20backsliding%20of%20democracy%20in%20India%20and%20capture%20of%20institutions%20curbs%20on%20freedom%20of%20press.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20create%20a%20narrative%20globally%2C%20which%20would%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20it%20can%20be%20effective%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20damage%20India%20and%20India's%20prospects%20of%20attracting%20foreign%20investment%20and%20everything%20else%20by%20giving%20the%20impression%20that%20India%20is%20sliding%20into%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20political%20and%20administrative%20system%20which%20is%20not%20very%20conducive%20to%20Western%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20added%2C%20finds%20resonance%20in%20UUS%20Boardrooms%2C%20though%20it%20has%20not%20got%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20influencing%20inves