%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscourse%20around%20menstruation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecame%20evident%20to%20him.%20So%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20ripples%20of%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20being%20catapulted%20across%20200%20slum%20areas%20in%20over%2026%20cities%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20changemaker%20is%20born%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Sandy%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Khanda.%20His%20childhood%20was%20spent%20helping%20his%20father%20take%20care%20of%20the%20paddy.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20would%20often%20hear%20of%20female%20foeticide%2C%20patriarchy%20and%20taboo%20around%20menstrual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAscribing%20his%20entrepreneurial%20relevance%20to%20his%20roots%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20these%20issues%20but%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20or%20resources%20back%20then.%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20where%20I%20was%20taught%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20career.%20But%20the%20accident%20changed%20everything.%20I%20saw%20this%20as%20the%20second%20chance%20that%20I%20was%20given%20to%20serve%20my%20community%3B%20a%20chance%20to%20utilise%20my%20life%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20focuses%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190014%2Fiit-girl-innovation-low-cost-zero-electricity-device-clean-sanitary-pads-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Slum%20to%20School%E2%80%99%20initiative%20is%20present%20in%2026%20slums%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20enrolling%2062%20childr