ic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20strand%20composition%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds%20a%20subtle%20texture%20to%20the%20overall%20monochromatic%2C%20industrial-themed%20office%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20OSB%20does%20manage%20to%20lend%20some%20bespoke%20detailing%20to%20the%20building%2C%20it%20is%20susceptible%20to%20moisture%20absorption.%20This%2C%20says%20Aameer%2C%20can%20affect%20its%20dimensional%20stability%20and%20performance%20over%20time.%20Another%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20since%20OSB%20is%20procured%20from%20trees%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverify%20the%20specific%20environmental%20certifications%20and%20sustainability%20attributes%20of%20the%20OSB%20product%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Compressed%20Stabilised%20Earth%20Bricks%20(CSEB)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20study%20underscored%2C%20%E2%80%9CCompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%20due%20to%20the%20lower%20amount%20of%20energy%20required%20for%20their%20production%2C%20lower%20cost%20and%20lower%20carbon%20footprint.%20Compared%20to%20cement%20concrete%2C%20CSEBs%20also%20require%20less%20embodied%20energy%2C%20with%20some%20authors%20indicating%20that%20only%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20production%20energy%20of%20cement%20concrete%20is%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20architects%20Rahul%20Kadri%2C%20Nithin%20Hosabettu%2C%20Sahil%20Bipin%20Deshpande%2C%20Viraj%20Naralkar%2C%20and%20Aakash%20Shrivastav%20of%20Mumbai-based%20IMK%20Architects%20were%20tasked%20with%20designing%20the%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%2C%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312182%2Fmaking-of-odisha-krushi-bhavan-sustainable-architecture-local-craftsmanship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20enthusiastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20do%20the%20bricks%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20structure%20but%20they%20also%20boast%2080%20percent%20less%20energy%20consumption%20while%20achieving%20thermal%20comfort.%20The%20architects%20share%20that%20the%20bricks%20they%20used%20were%20made%20using%20a%20natural%20mix%20of%20red%20soil%2C%20sand%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crumbled%20rock)%20stabilised%20with%20five%20percent%20cement.%20This%20ensured%20their%20durability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%20has%20been%20built%20with%20compressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20that%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%