A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20The%20APAAR%20Card%20Works%3A%20Answers%20to%20All%20Your%20Questions%20About%20This%20Student%20ID%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20why%20was%20it%20introduced%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20introduced%20the%20Automated%20Permanent%20Academic%20Account%20Registry%20(APAAR%20ID)%2C%20aligned%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20The%20initiative%20aims%20to%20simplify%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383777%2Fsabia-share-book-india-children-literacy-education-government-schools-volunteer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacademic%20journey%20for%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20a%20digital%20identifier%20that%20links%20their%20educational%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions%2C%20both%20within%20India%20and%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20type%20of%20academic%20information%20can%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20a%20unique%2012-digit%20code%20allowing%20students%20to%20digitally%20store%2C%20manage%2C%20and%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20academic%20information.%20This%20includes%20scorecards%2C%20marksheets%2C%20grade%20sheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20diplomas%2C%20certificates%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ensures%20smoother%20transitions%20between%20different%20educational%20stages%20and%20institutions%2C%20offering%20significant%20benefits%20for%20students%20pursuing%20education%20across%20various%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20access%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20specific%20process%20to%20follow%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPAAR%20integrates%20with%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC)%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accumulate%2C%20transfer%2C%20and%20redeem%20credits%20across%20institutions.%20This%20system%20not%20only%20facilitates%20credit%20transfers%20but%20also%20tracks%20academic%20achievements%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20their%20educational%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20students%20can%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20as%20it%20consolidates%20all%20their%20achievements%20onto%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20creating%20a%20comprehensive%20digital%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20requirements%20for%20applying%20for%20an%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20generating%20an%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20important%20prerequisites%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20UDISE%2B%20(Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20Plus)%20records%20must%20match%20exactly%20with%20the%20name%20as%20per%20their%20Aadhaar.%20This%20ensures%20consistency%20and%20accuracy%20in%20the%20identification%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Education%20Number%20(PEN)%20is%20mandatory%20for%20generating%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20It%20is%20a%20unique%20identification%20number%20for%20students%20across%20all%20the%20education%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20APAAR%20ID%20only%20useful%20for%20current%20students%2C%20or%20can%20it%20benefit%20graduates%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20beneficial%20not%20only%20for%20current%20students%20but%20also%20for%20graduates.%20For%20students%20like%20Krystelle%20Dsouza%2C%20a%20journalist%20pursuing%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20journalism%20at%20Mumbai%20University%2C%20this%20ID%20serves%20as%20a%20long-term%20academic%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20create%20my%20APAAR%20ID%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC).%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20step%20for%20students%20to%20have%20access%20to%20all%20of%20their%20degree%20certificates%20and%20anything%20they%E2%80%99ve%20accumulated%20throughout%20their%20academic%20trajectory%20in%20one%20place.%E2%80%9D%20This%20highlights%20how%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20helps%20graduates%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20achievements%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20easily%20accessible%2C%20even%20after%20completing%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20I%20need%20to%20register%20for%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20how%20do%20I%20get%20started%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20register%20for%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20To%20register%2C%20visit%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website%20%E2%80%93%20abc.gov.in%20and%20click%20on%20%E2%80%98My%20Account%2C%E2%80%99%20then%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98Student%E2%80%99%20option.%20Next%2C%20click%20%E2%80%98Sign%20up%E2%80%99%20and%20provide%20your%20mobile%20number%2C%20address%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217362%2Fhow-to-get-cbse-10-12-examination-marksheet-migration-certification-online-digilocker-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20a%20DigiLocker%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20logging%20in%20with%20your%20credentials%2C%20DigiLocker%20will%20prompt%20you%20to%20consent%20to%20share%20your%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20ABC%20for%20KYC%20verification.%20Once%20you%20agree%2C%20enter%20your%20academic%20details%2C%20such%20as%20your%20school%20or%20university%20name%2C%20class%2C%20and%20course.%20After%20submitting%20the%20form%2C%20your%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20will%20be%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20you%20download%20your%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20can%20be%20easily%20downloaded%20by%20logging%20into%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website.%20Once%20logged%20in%2C%20students%20can%20navigate%20to%20the%20dashboard%20and%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98APAAR%20card%20download%E2%80%99%20option.%20The%20card%20will%20then%20appear%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20downloaded%20or%20printed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20We%20will%20update%20the%20latest%20information%20about%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20when%20more%20details%20are%20revealed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733318268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-mobile-1732080263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20launched%20in%202023%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20provides%20a%20digital%20identity%20that%20helps%20students%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions.%20This%2012-digit%20ID%20consolidates%20information%20like%20marksheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements%20into%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20simplifying%20academic%20transitions%20and%20tracking%20progress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386210%2Fhow-apaar-id-works-answers-to-all-your-questions-about-this-student-id-system%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legal%20Expert%20Shares%20Tips%20for%20Resolving%20Disputes%20Outside%20the%20Courtroom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResolving%20disputes%20through%20traditional%20courts%20can%20be%20a%20daunting%20process%20%E2%80%94%20expensive%2C%20time-consuming%2C%20and%20stressful.%20Judicial%20Dispute%20Resolution%20(JDR)%20often%20drags%20on%20for%20years%2C%20exhausting%20resources%20and%20patience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20November%2015%2C%202024%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20district%20and%20subordinate%20courts%20face%20a%20staggering%204.53%20crore%20pending%20cases!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20did%20you%20know%20there%20are%20alternative%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresolve%20disputes%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20privately%2C%20and%20amicably%3F%20This%20is%20where%20Alternative%20Dispute%20Resolution%20(ADR)%20steps%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20ADR%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADR%20refers%20to%20methods%20of%20settling%20disputes%20without%20resorting%20to%20litigation.%20It%20encompasses%20various%20approaches%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357644%2Fsama-legal-tech-startup-resolves-civil-disputes-through-online-dispute-resolution-odr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediation%2C%20Conciliation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Negotiation%2C%20Lok%20Adalat%2C%20and%20Arbitration.%20These%20methods%20offer%20faster%2C%20more%20flexible%2C%20and%20cost-effective%20alternatives%20to%20conventional%20courtroom%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20JDR%2C%20clients%20depend%20heavily%20on%20advocates%20due%20to%20the%20formalities%20involved%20in%20litigation.%20But%20in%20ADR%2C%20like%20mediation%2C%20the%20processes%20are%20simple%20and%20it%20almost%20resembles%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20system%2C%20where%20both%20the%20parties%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20talk%20freely%20and%20solve%20their%20disputes%20without%20any%20hostility%2C%E2%80%9D%20A%20G%20Abhishek%2C%20a%20lawyer%20handling%20Supreme%20Court%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20(SLP)%20cases%2C%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADR%20offers%20numerous%20benefits%2C%20including%20confidentiality%2C%20faster%20resolutions%2C%20and%20tailored%20processes.%20It%20also%20helps%20preserve%20relationships%2C%20often%20strained%20in%20court%20battles.%20ADR%20is%20especially%20effective%20in%20business%2C%20employment%2C%20family%2C%20and%20consumer%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EArbitration%3A%20A%20closer%20look%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArbitration%20is%20a%20formalised%20ADR%20method%20where%20an%20independent%20arbitrator%20hears%20both%20sides%20and%20makes%20a%20decision%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20binding%20for%20both%20parties.%20Think%20of%20the%20arbitrator%20as%20a%20private%20judge%20who%20ensures%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20resolution%20without%20involving%20the%20formal%20court%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20works%20well%20for%20commercial%2C%20contractual%2C%20financial%2C%20intellectual%20property%2C%20and%20even%20international%20disputes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-768x862.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-150x168.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087.jpeg%201140w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20G%20Abhishek%2C%20a%20lawyer%20handling%20Supreme%20Court%20SLP%20cases%2C%20explains%20that%20ADR%20processes%20almost%20resemble%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20system.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CArbitration%20benefits%20courts%20by%20addressing%20less%20critical%20issues%20outside%20the%20courtroom%2C%20saving%20judicial%20time%20for%20more%20pressing%20cases.%20Consumers%20also%20gain%20quick%20and%20quality%20resolutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20advantages%20have%20prompted%20legislative%20reforms%20aimed%20at%20making%20arbitration%20more%20accessible%20and%20efficient%20in%20India.%20The%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20seeks%20to%20transform%20the%20country%20into%20a%20more%20arbitration-friendly%20jurisdiction.%20By%20reducing%20court%20involvement%20and%20aligning%20Indian%20arbitration%20laws%20with%20international%20standards%2C%20the%20Act%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20predictable%20legal%20framework%20for%20resolving%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20characteristics%20of%20arbitration%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Voluntary%20agreement%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArbitration%20typically%20stems%20from%20mutual%20consent%2C%20outlined%20in%20contracts%20that%20bind%20parties%20to%20settle%20disputes%20through%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Neutral%20arbitrator%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20third%20party%20%E2%80%94%20often%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20dispute%E2%80%99s%20subject%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20acts%20as%20an%20impartial%20decision-maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Private%20and%20confidential%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20Unlike%20court%20proceedings%2C%20arbitration%20is%20confidential%20and%20takes%20place%20in%20an%20arbitration%20centre%20which%20protects%20sensitive%20information%20and%20preserves%20business%20reputations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Binding%20decisions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20arbitrator%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20called%20an%20award%2C%20is%20usually%20final%20and%20enforceable%2C%20with%20limited%20grounds%20for%20appeal.%20This%20ensures%20a%20conclusive%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Flexibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Parties%20can%20tailor%20the%20process%2C%20including%20selecting%20arbitrators%2C%20and%20setting%20rules%20and%20timelines%2C%20making%20it%20faster%20and%20more%20adaptable%20than%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Cost-effective%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20often%20reduces%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20court%20battles%2C%20as%20the%20process%20is%20streamlined%20with%20fewer%20procedural%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20International%20applicability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20is%20widely%20recognised%20across%20borders%20through%20treaties%20like%20the%20New%20York%20Convention%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20resolving%20international%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20solve%20disputes%20via%20arbitration%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnybody%20who%20has%20mentioned%20in%20the%20agreement%20clause%20that%20their%20disputes%20will%20be%20solved%20via%20arbitration%20can%20approach%20the%20arbitration%20centres.%20The%20agreement%20must%20be%20submitted%20as%20proof%20for%20further%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20parties%20have%20not%20included%20an%20arbitration%20clause%20in%20their%20agreement%2C%20they%20can%20submit%20an%20application%20to%20the%20court%20under%20Section%2011%20of%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%20(1996)%2C%20requesting%20to%20fix%20an%20arbitration.%20Based%20on%20the%20technicalities%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20retired%20judge%20or%20anyone%20with%20equal%20expertise%20will%20be%20appointed%20as%20the%20arbitrator%20for%20the%20dispute%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F845779-icadr-international-centre-for-alternative-dispute-resolution-070819-1732877176-1733283364-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m