ncludes%20a%20library%20development%20programme%20for%20rural%20and%20remote%20schools%2C%20a%20teacher%20training%20programme%2C%20book%20fairs%2C%20and%20donation%20drives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%20to%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20done%20by%20SABIA%20in%20March%202022%20revealed%20that%20over%2050%20government%20schools%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20implement%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Padhe%20Bharat%20Badhe%20Bharat%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20government%20scheme%20which%20aims%20to%20provide%20extra%20reading%20material%20and%20inculcate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F207803%2Ftamil-nadu-barber-library-salon-discount-read-books-harsha-bhogle-viral-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20habit%20of%20reading%3C%2Fa%3E%20amongst%20the%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20even%20though%20there%20is%20a%20government%20scheme%20that%20wants%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem%20that%20has%20been%20identified%2C%20those%20books%20are%20never%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20something%20that%20we%20have%20been%20working%20towards%20diligently.%20We%20are%20making%20all%20stakeholders%20within%20the%20school%20system%2C%20the%20teachers%2C%20and%20principals%20understand%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20if%20the%20books%20are%20used%20and%20damaged.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20pointless%20to%20even%20have%20them%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%204110px)%20100vw%2C%204110px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG_3353-1_11zon-1732781104.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224110%5C%22%20